text:
Experience

Graphic, Web Designer
Freelance, Antananarivo, Madagascar May 2016-Aug 2023


Utilized advanced design software and industry best practices to produce innovative and effective designs for both digital and print platforms, for a monthly 3 to 4 clients
Engaged in a comprehensive design process, including research, ideation, wireframing, prototyping, and final design refinement in a team of +4 members
Demonstrated ability to drive brand recognition and increased audience engagement through effective design solutions on behalf of +25 happy clients



French Content Writer
ProcomNet, Antananarivo, Madagascar Jan 2016-Feb 2018


Engaged target audience over 96 French geographic departments, created engaging content, adapted to cultural nuances within tight deadlines
Conducted research, wrote compelling copy of +1,000 words daily, optimized for SEO, and proofread work
Improved website traffic, enhanced user experience, and established strong brand reputations on +15 websites



Graphic Designer
UNFPA, Antananarivo, Madagascar Jun 2015-Apr 2016


Communicated complex health and family planningmessages over 6 regions in Madagascar on print and web media with visually appealing designs, met deadlines, and adapted to changes
Conducted research, brainstormed ideas, created wireframes and mockups, developed final designs, refined media products for 5 main programs
Achieved effective communication, brand recognition, and increased engagement from 108,180 children and women received health and prenatal care
